ABINIT is an atomic-scale simulation software suite.

Please see the file COPYING for copying conditions.

Please see the files in the Infos/ directory for documentation that can be
printed with TeX, or read with a web browser. There will be man pages soon.

See the file INSTALL for generic compilation and installation instructions,
and the file INSTALLME for instructions specific to ABINIT.

Additional information can be found on the ABINIT website:

	http://www.abinit.org/

Please read carefully the Infos/problem_report before reporting bugs to
Xavier Gonze <gonze@pcpm.ucl.ac.be>.



ABINIT-related mailing lists
----------------------------

ABINIT has several mailing lists, all hosted by abinit.org. They do not
allow posts from non-subscribers.

announce@abinit.org:

    TODO

forum@abinit.org:

    TODO

developers@abinit.org:

    The mailing list for developers. This is the preferred place
    to post bug reports and suggestions, as well as discuss
    development-related matters.

    To post to the list, send mail to <developers@abinit.org>. To
    subscribe, send mail to <developers-subscribe@abinit.org>.

    This mailing list is archived at:

    http://www.abinit.org/wws/arc/forum

